Package: datelife
Title: Go from a List of Taxa or a Tree to a Chronogram using Open Scientific Data on Time of Lineage Divergence
Version: 0.6.0
Maintainer: Luna L. Sanchez Reyes <sanchez.reyes.luna@gmail.com>
