Description: Methods and workflows to get dated phylogenetic trees, aka chronograms,
    using open scientific data on time of lineage divergence.
    This package constitutes the main underlying code of the DateLife web services
    at www.datelife.org.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
